description:
Established
in 2000, Right Power Technology Sdn Bhd stands as a leading producer
and distributor of reliable, affordable, and efficient UPS systems.
With over 20 years of experience, Right Power excels in delivering
power protection solutions and maintenance services for critical
mission facilities across the business, education, and commercial
sectors.
Right Power offers a comprehensive
range of products, including Line Interactive Simulated Sinewave,
True Online Sinewave, and Smart Pure Sinewave UPS systems.
Additionally, we provide a full suite of heavy-duty and
high-performance Industrial Automatic Voltage Regulators (AVRs), with
capacities ranging from 800VA to 10,000KVA.
Our extensive portfolio ensures total
data center power protection, featuring VRLA AGM and Lithium-ion
batteries, Battery Monitoring Systems (BMS), reliable Frequency
Converters, and scalable Modular Data Center solutions.
